data.description: FOR SALE! Currently an Investment Home; with a tenant that doesn't want to move. Are you an investor? Then this the home is for you. If you're not an investor, it's still a great deal! Well maintained 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Home in East Broken Arrow. Spacious 2 Car Garage. Large Fenced Quarter Acre Corner Lot. Open Living Area with lots of Natural Light and Vaulted ceiling. Wood Burning Fireplace. Kitchen has Stainless Steel Fridge, Dishwasher, Disposal, Range/Oven & Microwave. Master with Private Bath and Walk-In Closet. Hallway Bath serves the remaining 2 Bedrooms. Inside Utility; Electric AND Gas connection for Dryer. Lots of Storage. Large Fenced Backyard. What a great neighborhood!
